A simple and responsive web-based Password Generator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This tool allows users to generate strong, random passwords based on customizable options like length and character types.

Features

- Generate secure and random passwords
- Choose password length
- Toggle inclusion of:
  - Uppercase letters
  - Lowercase letters
  - Numbers
  - Special characters
- Copy password to clipboard
- Responsive design for all screen sizes

